{
  "openapi": "3.0.3",
  "info": {
    "title": "personal_assistant - OJ 业务接口",
    "version": "1.0.0",
    "description": "覆盖业务路由中的 5 个 OJ 相关接口，可直接导入 Apifox。\n\n接口范围：\n- POST /oj/bind\n- POST /oj/lanqiao/bind\n- POST /oj/stats\n- POST /oj/ranking_list\n- POST /oj/curve\n\n统一约束：\n- 以上接口都注册在 BusinessGroup，下游统一经过 JWTAuth 和 ActiveUserMW。\n- 当前 JWT 中间件支持两种 header 取 token：Authorization: Bearer <access_token> 或 x-access-token: <access_token>；同时也兼容 Cookie 中的 x-access-token。\n- JWT 缺失、Token 无效、Token 过期时，中间件返回旧版响应壳，HTTP 状态码仍为 200。\n- 账号被禁用或非 active 时，ActiveUserMW 返回 HTTP 401 的 BizResponse。\n\n实现现状说明：\n- /oj/bind、/oj/stats、/oj/ranking_list 使用旧版响应壳：code + data + messages/error。\n- /oj/lanqiao/bind、/oj/curve 使用新版 BizResponse：code + success + message + data + timestamp。\n- 本文件按仓库当前真实实现生成，方便直接导入 Apifox 联调。"
  },
  "servers": [
    {
      "url": "http://127.0.0.1:9000",
      "description": "本地开发环境，请按实际地址修改"
    }
  ],
  "tags": [
    {
      "name": "用户基础信息",
      "description": "当前登录用户的 OJ 账号绑定接口，包含洛谷/力扣通用绑定和蓝桥专用绑定。"
    },
    {
      "name": "OJ业务",
      "description": "当前登录用户的 OJ 统计、排行榜和刷题曲线查询接口。"
    }
  ],
  "security": [
    {
      "BearerAuth": []
    },
    {
      "AccessTokenHeader": []
    }
  ],
  "paths": {
    "/oj/bind": {
      "post": {
        "tags": [
          "用户基础信息"
        ],
        "summary": "绑定洛谷或力扣账号",
        "description": "绑定当前登录用户的洛谷或力扣公开账号。\n\n平台规则：\n- platform=luogu：identifier 必须传洛谷用户 UID 字符串，例如 \"123456\"；不是用户名，也不是题号。\n- platform=leetcode：identifier 必须传 LeetCode 用户公开 slug，例如 \"alice-cn\"。\n- 蓝桥不走这个接口，必须使用 /oj/lanqiao/bind。\n\n换绑和冷却规则：\n- 已绑定同平台账号时，服务端会检查绑定冷却期，默认按 global.Config.System.BindCoolDownHours 控制；配置缺失时默认 24 小时。\n- 冷却期内重复绑定会返回 40005。\n- 冷却期结束后，如果改绑为新的 identifier，旧的题目关系和缓存会被清理后重建。\n\n响应规则：\n- 成功返回旧版响应壳：code/data/messages。\n- 参数绑定失败、业务失败、JWT 缺失或 Token 无效同样可能返回 HTTP 200，请以前端业务码为准。\n- 账号被禁用时返回 HTTP 401 的 BizResponse。",
        "operationId": "BindOJAccount",
        "requestBody": {
          "required": true,
          "content": {
            "application/json": {
              "schema": {
                "$ref": "#/components/schemas/BindOJAccountReq"
              },
              "examples": {
                "绑定力扣账号": {
                  "value": {
                    "platform": "leetcode",
                    "identifier": "alice-cn"
                  }
                },
                "绑定洛谷账号": {
                  "value": {
                    "platform": "luogu",
                    "identifier": "123456"
                  }
                }
              }
            }
          }
        },
        "responses": {
          "200": {
            "description": "成功、参数绑定失败、业务失败、JWT 缺失或 Token 无效都可能返回 HTTP 200；请结合 code 与返回壳结构判断。",
            "content": {
              "application/json": {
                "schema": {
                  "oneOf": [
                    {
                      "$ref": "#/components/schemas/LegacySuccessResponseBindOJ"
                    },
                    {
                      "$ref": "#/components/schemas/LegacyErrorResponse"
                    },
                    {
                      "$ref": "#/components/schemas/LegacyTokenErrorResponse"
                    }
                  ]
                },
                "examples": {
                  "绑定成功-力扣": {
                    "value": {
                      "code": 0,
                      "data": {
                        "platform": "leetcode",
                        "identifier": "alice-cn",
                        "real_name": "Alice",
                        "user_avatar": "https://cdn.example.com/avatar/alice.png",
                        "passed_number": 428,
                        "submit_success_count": 0,
                        "submit_failed_count": 0
                      },
                      "messages": "绑定成功"
                    }
                  },
                  "绑定成功-洛谷": {
                    "value": {
                      "code": 0,
                      "data": {
                        "platform": "luogu",
                        "identifier": "123456",
                        "real_name": "洛谷用户A",
                        "user_avatar": "https://cdn.example.com/avatar/luogu-a.png",
                        "passed_number": 213,
                        "submit_success_count": 0,
                        "submit_failed_count": 0
                      },
                      "messages": "绑定成功"
                    }
                  },
                  "参数绑定失败": {
                    "value": {
                      "code": 10002,
                      "data": null,
                      "error": "绑定数据错误: Key: 'BindOJAccountReq.Platform' Error:Field validation for 'Platform' failed on the 'oneof' tag"
                    }
                  },
                  "标识为空白": {
                    "value": {
                      "code": 40004,
                      "data": null,
                      "error": "绑定OJ账号失败: invalid identifier"
                    }
                  },
                  "冷却期内重复绑定": {
                    "value": {
                      "code": 40005,
                      "data": null,
                      "error": "绑定OJ账号失败: bind operation is in cooldown"
                    }
                  },
                  "洛谷账户受保护或远程抓取失败": {
                    "value": {
                      "code": 10004,
                      "data": null,
                      "error": "绑定OJ账号失败: 由于您的洛谷账户受到官方保护，暂时无法爬取，请联系管理员"
                    }
                  },
                  "未登录-缺少AccessToken": {
                    "value": {
                      "code": 11005,
                      "data": {
                        "message": "Access token is required",
                        "reload": true
                      },
                      "error": "Access token is required"
                    }
                  }
                }
              }
            }
          },
          "401": {
            "description": "账号活跃态校验失败，例如账号已禁用。",
            "content": {
              "application/json": {
                "schema": {
                  "$ref": "#/components/schemas/BizUnauthorizedResponse"
                },
                "example": {
                  "code": 11000,
                  "success": false,
                  "message": "账号已禁用",
                  "data": null,
                  "timestamp": 1773399170123
                }
              }
            }
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "/oj/lanqiao/bind": {
      "post": {
        "tags": [
          "用户基础信息"
        ],
        "summary": "绑定蓝桥账号",
        "description": "绑定当前登录用户的蓝桥账号。\n\n请求规则：\n- 需要传手机号和密码。\n- phone 支持常见输入形式，服务端会归一化为 11 位手机号；例如 \"+86 13800138000\"、\"86 13800138000\"、\"138-0013-8000\" 都会被清洗。\n- password 不能为空。\n\n安全与数据语义：\n- 服务端不会明文存储手机号和密码，会转为哈希和密文存储。\n- 返回的 identifier 是脱敏手机号，例如 \"138****8000\"。\n- passed_number 表示蓝桥去重后的通过题总数，是业务真相。\n- submit_success_count 和 submit_failed_count 表示蓝桥远端提交统计，不等于通过题总数。\n\n冲突与错误：\n- 同一组蓝桥账号凭据只能绑定到一个系统用户；若已被其他用户绑定，返回 40002。\n- 远端鉴权失败时返回 40007。\n- 远端同步失败时返回 40006。\n\n响应规则：\n- 成功和大多数业务失败返回新版 BizResponse。\n- JWT 缺失或 Token 无效时仍可能收到旧版认证失败响应壳，HTTP 状态码为 200。",
        "operationId": "BindLanqiaoAccount",
        "requestBody": {
          "required": true,
          "content": {
            "application/json": {
              "schema": {
                "$ref": "#/components/schemas/BindLanqiaoAccountReq"
              },
              "examples": {
                "标准写法": {
                  "value": {
                    "phone": "13800138000",
                    "password": "LanQiao@2026"
                  }
                },
                "带国家码写法": {
                  "value": {
                    "phone": "+86 13800138000",
                    "password": "LanQiao@2026"
                  }
                }
              }
            }
          }
        },
        "responses": {
          "200": {
            "description": "成功、业务失败、JWT 缺失或 Token 无效都可能返回 HTTP 200；请结合 code 与返回壳结构判断。",
            "content": {
              "application/json": {
                "schema": {
                  "oneOf": [
                    {
                      "$ref": "#/components/schemas/BizSuccessResponseBindLanqiao"
                    },
                    {
                      "$ref": "#/components/schemas/BizErrorResponse"
                    },
                    {
                      "$ref": "#/components/schemas/LegacyTokenErrorResponse"
                    }
                  ]
                },
                "examples": {
                  "绑定成功": {
                    "value": {
                      "code": 0,
                      "success": true,
                      "message": "操作成功",
                      "data": {
                        "platform": "lanqiao",
                        "identifier": "138****8000",
                        "real_name": "",
                        "user_avatar": "",
                        "passed_number": 56,
                        "submit_success_count": 132,
                        "submit_failed_count": 17
                      },
                      "timestamp": 1773399180123
                    }
                  },
                  "手机号格式非法": {
                    "value": {
                      "code": 40007,
                      "success": false,
                      "message": "蓝桥手机号格式不合法",
                      "data": null,
                      "timestamp": 1773399181123
                    }
                  },
                  "密码为空": {
                    "value": {
                      "code": 40007,
                      "success": false,
                      "message": "蓝桥密码不能为空",
                      "data": null,
                      "timestamp": 1773399182123
                    }
                  },
                  "账号已被其他用户绑定": {
                    "value": {
                      "code": 40002,
                      "success": false,
                      "message": "OJ账号已绑定",
                      "data": null,
                      "timestamp": 1773399183123
                    }
                  },
                  "账号或密码错误": {
                    "value": {
                      "code": 40007,
                      "success": false,
                      "message": "蓝桥账号或密码不正确",
                      "data": null,
                      "timestamp": 1773399184123
                    }
                  },
                  "蓝桥远端同步失败": {
                    "value": {
                      "code": 40006,
                      "success": false,
                      "message": "OJ数据同步失败",
                      "data": null,
                      "timestamp": 1773399185123
                    }
                  },
                  "未登录-缺少AccessToken": {
                    "value": {
                      "code": 11005,
                      "data": {
                        "message": "Access token is required",
                        "reload": true
                      },
                      "error": "Access token is required"
                    }
                  }
                }
              }
            }
          },
          "401": {
            "description": "账号活跃态校验失败，例如账号已禁用。",
            "content": {
              "application/json": {
                "schema": {
                  "$ref": "#/components/schemas/BizUnauthorizedResponse"
                },
                "example": {
                  "code": 11000,
                  "success": false,
                  "message": "账号已禁用",
                  "data": null,
                  "timestamp": 1773399186123
                }
              }
            }
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "/oj/stats": {
      "post": {
        "tags": [
          "OJ业务"
        ],
        "summary": "获取当前用户 OJ 统计信息",
        "description": "查询当前登录用户在指定 OJ 平台上的基础统计卡片。\n\n平台规则：\n- platform=leetcode：返回用户 slug、昵称、头像、总通过题数。\n- platform=luogu：返回洛谷 UID、昵称、头像、通过题数。\n- platform=lanqiao：返回脱敏手机号、去重通过题总数，以及蓝桥提交成功和失败统计。\n\n字段语义：\n- passed_number 是统一的通过题总数字段。\n- submit_success_count 和 submit_failed_count 只有蓝桥有业务含义，其他平台固定返回 0。\n- 蓝桥的 passed_number 来源于题目事实表去重统计，不等于 submit_success_count。\n\n响应规则：\n- 当前接口成功返回旧版响应壳：code/data/messages。\n- 未绑定目标平台账号时返回 40001，但仍是旧版失败响应壳。\n- 参数缺失或非法会在 Controller 绑定阶段返回 10002。",
        "operationId": "GetOJStats",
        "requestBody": {
          "required": true,
          "content": {
            "application/json": {
              "schema": {
                "$ref": "#/components/schemas/OJStatsReq"
              },
              "examples": {
                "查询力扣统计": {
                  "value": {
                    "platform": "leetcode"
                  }
                },
                "查询洛谷统计": {
                  "value": {
                    "platform": "luogu"
                  }
                },
                "查询蓝桥统计": {
                  "value": {
                    "platform": "lanqiao"
                  }
                }
              }
            }
          }
        },
        "responses": {
          "200": {
            "description": "成功、参数绑定失败、业务失败、JWT 缺失或 Token 无效都可能返回 HTTP 200；请结合 code 与返回壳结构判断。",
            "content": {
              "application/json": {
                "schema": {
                  "oneOf": [
                    {
                      "$ref": "#/components/schemas/LegacySuccessResponseStats"
                    },
                    {
                      "$ref": "#/components/schemas/LegacyErrorResponse"
                    },
                    {
                      "$ref": "#/components/schemas/LegacyTokenErrorResponse"
                    }
                  ]
                },
                "examples": {
                  "查询成功-力扣": {
                    "value": {
                      "code": 0,
                      "data": {
                        "platform": "leetcode",
                        "identifier": "alice-cn",
                        "real_name": "Alice",
                        "user_avatar": "https://cdn.example.com/avatar/alice.png",
                        "passed_number": 428,
                        "submit_success_count": 0,
                        "submit_failed_count": 0
                      },
                      "messages": "获取成功"
                    }
                  },
                  "查询成功-洛谷": {
                    "value": {
                      "code": 0,
                      "data": {
                        "platform": "luogu",
                        "identifier": "123456",
                        "real_name": "洛谷用户A",
                        "user_avatar": "https://cdn.example.com/avatar/luogu-a.png",
                        "passed_number": 213,
                        "submit_success_count": 0,
                        "submit_failed_count": 0
                      },
                      "messages": "获取成功"
                    }
                  },
                  "查询成功-蓝桥": {
                    "value": {
                      "code": 0,
                      "data": {
                        "platform": "lanqiao",
                        "identifier": "138****8000",
                        "real_name": "",
                        "user_avatar": "",
                        "passed_number": 56,
                        "submit_success_count": 132,
                        "submit_failed_count": 17
                      },
                      "messages": "获取成功"
                    }
                  },
                  "目标平台未绑定": {
                    "value": {
                      "code": 40001,
                      "data": null,
                      "error": "获取用户卡片信息失败: oj account not bound"
                    }
                  },
                  "参数绑定失败": {
                    "value": {
                      "code": 10002,
                      "data": null,
                      "error": "参数错误: Key: 'OJStatsReq.Platform' Error:Field validation for 'Platform' failed on the 'oneof' tag"
                    }
                  },
                  "未登录-缺少AccessToken": {
                    "value": {
                      "code": 11005,
                      "data": {
                        "message": "Access token is required",
                        "reload": true
                      },
                      "error": "Access token is required"
                    }
                  }
                }
              }
            }
          },
          "401": {
            "description": "账号活跃态校验失败，例如账号已禁用。",
            "content": {
              "application/json": {
                "schema": {
                  "$ref": "#/components/schemas/BizUnauthorizedResponse"
                },
                "example": {
                  "code": 11000,
                  "success": false,
                  "message": "账号已禁用",
                  "data": null,
                  "timestamp": 1773399190123
                }
              }
            }
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "/oj/ranking_list": {
      "post": {
        "tags": [
          "OJ业务"
        ],
        "summary": "查询 OJ 排行榜",
        "description": "查询指定平台的排行榜。\n\n请求参数：\n- platform：必填，支持 luogu / leetcode / lanqiao。\n- page：页码，默认 1。\n- page_size：每页条数，默认 20，最大 100。\n- scope：榜单范围，支持 current_org / all_members / org；默认 current_org。\n- org_id：仅当 scope=org 时需要传入。\n\n权限语义：\n- all_members：查询全体成员总榜。\n- current_org：查询当前组织榜；若当前组织本身就是内置全体成员组织，服务端会自动映射到总榜。\n- org：查询指定组织榜；普通用户只能查询自己仍为 active 成员的组织，super_admin 可以查询任意组织。\n\n排名语义：\n- 排行榜基于 Redis ZSet 倒序查询，分数越高越靠前。\n- total_passed 是该平台的排行榜分值。\n- platform_details 只会填充当前 platform 对应的一个字段。\n\n响应规则：\n- 当前接口使用旧版响应壳。\n- scope、org_id 等大多数业务校验失败目前会落到 10004，并把具体原因拼在 error 字段中。",
        "operationId": "GetOJRankingList",
        "requestBody": {
          "required": true,
          "content": {
            "application/json": {
              "schema": {
                "$ref": "#/components/schemas/OJRankingListReq"
              },
              "examples": {
                "当前组织-蓝桥榜": {
                  "value": {
                    "page": 1,
                    "page_size": 20,
                    "platform": "lanqiao",
                    "scope": "current_org"
                  }
                },
                "全体成员-力扣总榜": {
                  "value": {
                    "page": 1,
                    "page_size": 20,
                    "platform": "leetcode",
                    "scope": "all_members"
                  }
                },
                "指定组织-洛谷榜": {
                  "value": {
                    "page": 1,
                    "page_size": 20,
                    "platform": "luogu",
                    "scope": "org",
                    "org_id": 39
                  }
                }
              }
            }
          }
        },
        "responses": {
          "200": {
            "description": "成功、参数绑定失败、业务失败、JWT 缺失或 Token 无效都可能返回 HTTP 200；请结合 code 与返回壳结构判断。",
            "content": {
              "application/json": {
                "schema": {
                  "oneOf": [
                    {
                      "$ref": "#/components/schemas/LegacySuccessResponseRanking"
                    },
                    {
                      "$ref": "#/components/schemas/LegacyErrorResponse"
                    },
                    {
                      "$ref": "#/components/schemas/LegacyTokenErrorResponse"
                    }
                  ]
                },
                "examples": {
                  "查询成功-蓝桥当前组织榜": {
                    "value": {
                      "code": 0,
                      "data": {
                        "list": [
                          {
                            "rank": 1,
                            "user_id": 12,
                            "real_name": "alice",
                            "avatar": "https://cdn.example.com/avatar/alice.png",
                            "total_passed": 56,
                            "platform_details": {
                              "lanqiao": 56
                            }
                          },
                          {
                            "rank": 2,
                            "user_id": 18,
                            "real_name": "bob",
                            "avatar": "https://cdn.example.com/avatar/bob.png",
                            "total_passed": 48,
                            "platform_details": {
                              "lanqiao": 48
                            }
                          }
                        ],
                        "my_rank": {
                          "rank": 7,
                          "total_passed": 31
                        },
                        "total": 86
                      },
                      "messages": "获取成功"
                    }
                  },
                  "查询成功-力扣总榜": {
                    "value": {
                      "code": 0,
                      "data": {
                        "list": [
                          {
                            "rank": 1,
                            "user_id": 3,
                            "real_name": "charlie",
                            "avatar": "https://cdn.example.com/avatar/charlie.png",
                            "total_passed": 428,
                            "platform_details": {
                              "leetcode": 428
                            }
                          }
                        ],
                        "my_rank": {
                          "rank": 19,
                          "total_passed": 211
                        },
                        "total": 120
                      },
                      "messages": "获取成功"
                    }
                  },
                  "缺少platform": {
                    "value": {
                      "code": 40003,
                      "data": null,
                      "error": "获取排行榜失败: invalid platform"
                    }
                  },
                  "scope为org但缺少org_id": {
                    "value": {
                      "code": 10004,
                      "data": null,
                      "error": "获取排行榜失败: org_id is required for org scope"
                    }
                  },
                  "无权查询指定组织": {
                    "value": {
                      "code": 10004,
                      "data": null,
                      "error": "获取排行榜失败: user organization not active"
                    }
                  },
                  "未登录-缺少AccessToken": {
                    "value": {
                      "code": 11005,
                      "data": {
                        "message": "Access token is required",
                        "reload": true
                      },
                      "error": "Access token is required"
                    }
